<p>Most link building guides ignore the easiest backlinks available. Document sharing sites for backlinks give you free, high-authority links from domains with DA 80-100. All you do is upload content you already have.</p>
<p>We mapped 100+ document sharing sites across 10 content types. PDF submission sites, presentation platforms, infographic directories, video hosts, podcast directories, image sharing sites, code repositories, design platforms, academic archives, and ebook distributors. The first 27 get detailed breakdowns. The rest are organized by category in tables with DA scores, link types, and costs.</p>
<p><a href="https://backlinko.com/search-engine-ranking">95% of web pages have zero backlinks</a>. These 27 platforms fix that problem without cold outreach, guest posting fees, or agency retainers.</p>
<p>Here is what you will learn:</p>
<ul>
<li>100+ document sharing sites organized by content type</li>
<li>Which platforms give dofollow vs nofollow backlinks</li>
<li>How to repurpose one blog post into 6 uploadable formats</li>
