<h2>How to Repurpose One Blog Post Into 6 Uploadable Formats</h2>
<p>Most people think document sharing requires creating new content from scratch. It does not. One blog post can become 6 different uploads across all the platforms listed above.</p>
<p>Here is the conversion framework:</p>
